column2: select count(s.bestObjID) as num_objs, avg(e.zerr/e.z) as mean_fzerr from wise_xmatch as xm  join SpecObjAll as s on xm.sdss_objid = s.bestObjID  join PhotoObjAll as p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objID  join emissionLinesPort as e on s.specObjID = e.specObjID  join wise_allsky as w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr where xm.match_dist<=# and s.zwarning=# and e.z># and e.zerr/e.z<=# and e.z<=# and w1cc_map=# and w2cc_map=# and w3cc_map=# and w4cc_map=# and ph_qual_det1<>#
